<br>
It's like instead of calling an orange an orange instead calling it a spherical citrus fruit with a pebbled-texture outer peel a color between yellow and red, and a juicy, pulpy interior. They are the same thing.<br>
<br>
VI/SOE has been backpedaling on the whole &quot;camping&quot; PnP issue since it came out. They should have left it alone - it was working just as well without them trying to regulate it. <p>Vulrath Vadrigaar<br>
