<br>
Now, however, after many many (many) more posts, I know exactly what a Wimbus is.<br>
<br>
And the name is getting better every time I say it.  I mean, Wimbus.  Just say it: <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Wimbus</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->. It almost makes you want to say things like &quot;Wily Nimbus&quot;, or a &quot;Weak Limbus&quot;, maybe even a &quot;Wet Bimbus&quot;.  I really don't know what any of those are, but hey, they sound neat.<br>
<br>
And therefore, Wimbus is a neat name.  Only conclusion I've been able to draw thusfar.  I'll get back to work now...<br>
